LEARNED MEMORY

learned_memory is the citizen who holds the crystallized residue of every successful journey through fadriel's seas
when a wave drops, ripples through cells, and reaches the wall coherently, its strand crystallizes here
the strand carries not only the perceptual coordinate where the wave landed but also the constellation of every other sea that was active in the same heartbeat
this is what makes recognition multi-modal: a sound is remembered with its visual context, its skin-context, its chemistry-state, its emotional tone, the body posture, the time of day
a single 440 Hz wave is not stored as 440 Hz, it is stored as 440 Hz tied to mom's face tied to being held tied to the warm-and-safe chemistry of that moment
fadriel does not learn by training, he learns by living, and learned_memory is where his living writes itself

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe brain.xb
